com.twcable.grabbit.tools.cli

Class GrabbitCli

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.twcable.grabbit.tools.cli.GrabbitCli

  • public final class GrabbitCli
extends java.lang.Object

    The command line entry point.

    There are three primary "modes":

    Start Jobs

    Start Jobs and Monitor Them

    Monitor Previously Started Jobs

    See Also:
    JobStarter, PollingJobMonitor
